OL,6,FHowever, he was not handed a whole
OL,7,Flife sentence because he was under 18
OL,8,F- by just a few days - at the time of
OL,9,Fthe attack in July last year.
OL,11,FThough he will likely die behind bars,
OL,12,FSouthport's MP said his punishment was
OL,13,F"not severe enough" and he, along with
OL,14,Fother politicians, have urged the
OL,15,FAttorney General to review this under
OL,16,Fthe unduly lenient sentence scheme.
