OL,6,FThe Attorney General confirmed it will
OL,7,Freview Rudakubana's sentence and will
OL,8,Fhave 28 days to consider the case,
OL,9,Fbefore deciding whether to refer it to
OL,10,Fthe Court of Appeal.
OL,12,FThis has led to wider calls for a
OL,13,Fsentencing review to extended whole
OL,14,Flife terms to under-18s.
OL,16,FDefence Secretary John Healey
OL,17,Fsuggested international law prevents
OL,18,FBritain from imposing whole life terms
OL,19,Fto under-18s and pointed to a UN
OL,20,Fconvention on children's rights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
